data.description: This stunning 2-story home, nestled on a corner lot spanning 3/4 of an acre. Step into the two-story foyer and dining area, and office area with custom built-in shelving. The family room has a cozy stone fireplace, while the expansive island kitchen has plenty of cabinet space,  granite countertops and opens into the family room. The large primary suite features bay windows, a luxurious master bath with separate tub and shower, double sinks, and a large master closet with custom built-in shelving. Ascend the beautiful stairs to discover a family game room with access to a private balcony, three additional bedrooms, and a secondary bath with double sinks. New roof added 2 years ago! Easy access to 45! This beautiful property is ready to make your own.
